title: French King Cake ! Classic and Twisted versions...
description:
Video recipe on how to make a French king cake , galette des rois ou gateau des rois. Puff pastry and almonds cream make it a delicious and crispy cake, so easy to make ! Love you guys, it's good to see you back :) Celebrate the Epiphany !

Also a nicely twisted version with Moroccan vibes, cinnamon, and orange blossom water and phylo / filo pastry instead of puff pastry.
